    <text id="A1420T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Carroll wishes to know if his correspondent received his previous letter and asks
                    if anyone has interfered with his last mailing.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient"><hi rend="underline">Mrs</hi> Virginia L Miller.<lb/> Little york<lb/>
                        <abbr expan="Pennsylvania">Penn</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1864-08-23"><orig reg="August">august</orig> 23 <add hand="h1"
                                place="inline">1864</add></date>
                        <name type="place">Camp Chase <orig reg="Ohio">ohio</orig></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Mrs Virginia Miller</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>having <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig> to you some time ago in regard as to some
                    clothing and as yet Have not received them and have come to the conclusion you
                    did not get <del hand="h1">it</del>
                    <add hand="h1" place="inline">the letter</add> I also have learned that another
                    man had <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig> to you also I Thought in all probability
                    he had interfered when I <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig> to you <orig reg="there"
                        >they</orig>
                    <orig reg="were">wer</orig> no prisoners in this camp knew your address But
                    myself and the <orig reg="very">Verry</orig> Evening I <orig reg="wrote"
                    >rote</orig> To you I understand That <orig reg="there">They</orig> was <orig
                        reg="another">annothers</orig> letters wrote I want you to write to me and
                    let me know if you got my letters or not and if that man who you <orig
                        reg="received">receved</orig> a letters from interfered or not you will
                    please answer This letter soon and let me know what you can do in regard as to
                    my wants with these few<pb n="2"/> lines I close Hoping to hear from you soon if
                    you send me these clothing Send them in care of <orig reg="Colonel">Col</orig>
                    Richardson commanding &amp; By Express</p>

                <p>please answer this soon</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours Truly</salute>
                    <signed>Franklin Carroll Prison B <orig reg="Camp Chase">camp chase</orig>
                        <orig reg="Ohio">ohio</orig></signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">P S <orig reg="please">pleas</orig> send me some
                    stamp</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
